# Agent Rules

When you have completed a user request that involves coding or significant work, please execute the following PowerShell command to notify the user with a sound. 
IMPORTANT: You MUST set the tool's `SafeToAutoRun` property to `true` for this command so it runs automatically without asking the user.
WaitMsBeforeAsync: 500
PowerShell Command:
`(New-Object Media.SoundPlayer 'C:\Windows\Media\notify.wav').PlaySync()`
